I doubt if you relly want this, but it sure is possible.
Just add two macros:

/def -mregexp -h"SEND ^$" tmp1 = /send %last
/def -mregexp -h"SEND ^[^$]" tmp2 = /set last=%0%;/send %last

And to send an empty line, you would /send.
Note that /send will never activate a SEND hook.

