	You've asked it to match on the string "%CODE: ".  To have tf do
substitutions into those args, you can either use /eval or nest your
macro creation in another macro.  In both cases, you'd need to double
any %'s that occur in macro after the =.

/eval \
    /def -mregexp -t'%CODE: ' =\
        /echo I got the code! -- %%1

Or similar.

