Questions like that seem to dominate the mailing list...

Anyway, if you want to trigger that any time you're within 20 of your
possible mana, use:

/def -mregexp -t'H:([0-9]+)\(([0-9]+)\) M:([0-9]+)\(([0-9]+)\)
V:([0-9]+)\(([0-9]+)\)' = /if (0+{P3} >= {P4}-20) /fsc%;/endif

[that's all one line, except to netscape...]

