just want to do it anytime you're over 200 mana,

/def -mregexp -t'H:([0-9]+)\(([0-9]+)\) M:([0-9]+)\(([0-9]+)\)
V:([0-9]+)\(([0-9]+)\)' = /if (0+{P3} >= 200) /fsc%;/endif

