	You are going to have to use a prompt hook to do this.  Triggers
aren't called on the partial line.  You should be able to say:

-mregexp -F -p50 -h"PROMPT ^\| ([0-9]+)H ([0-9]+)E ([0-9]+)V [^>]*> "

